OL,3,CPolice officers who fail vetting to be
OL,4,Cautomatically sacked under new rules
OL,6,FPolice officers who fail background
OL,7,Fchecks will be automatically sacked
OL,8,Funder new rules aimed at restoring
OL,9,Fpublic confidence in policing.
OL,11,FNew measures will be introduced to
OL,12,FParliament on Wednesday, making it a
OL,13,Flegal requirement for serving police
OL,14,Fofficers to pass background checks.
OL,16,FWhen the reformed police dismissal
OL,17,Fsystem comes into force from May 14,
OL,18,Fpolice chiefs will also have the power
OL,19,Fto get rid of officers deemed unfit to
OL,20,Fserve.
