OL,6,FIn February, a Metropolitan Police
OL,7,Fofficer accused of sexual offences,
OL,8,FSergeant Lino Di Maria, successfully
OL,9,Fmounted a legal challenge after having
OL,10,Fhis vetting removed over the
OL,11,Fallegations, which he denies.
OL,13,FHe was found to have no case to answer
OL,14,Fin respect of misconduct allegations,
OL,15,Fand argued that having his vetting
OL,16,Fremoved without the accusations being
OL,17,Fproved is a breach of his right to a
OL,18,Ffair trial.
