OL,6,FThe force confirmed that it had now
OL,7,Fbeen granted leave to appeal against
OL,8,Fthe High Court judgment on Thursday
OL,9,Fafter it was deemed a matter of public
OL,10,Fimportance.
OL,12,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said: "In
OL,13,Frecent years, serious cases which have
OL,14,Fbadly failed all proper policing
OL,15,Fstandards have damaged public trust in
OL,16,Fthe officers who are supposed to
OL,17,Fprotect them, and undermined the
OL,18,Fmajority of brave, committed officers
OL,19,Fwho work tirelessly to keep us safe.
