OL,3,CPolice officers who fail vetting to be
OL,4,Cautomatically sacked under new rules
OL,6,F"It is simply not acceptable that
OL,7,Fofficers who are clearly unfit to
OL,8,Fserve or pose a risk to their
OL,9,Fcolleagues cannot be removed.
OL,11,F"That's why these new rules are
OL,12,Fessential and it is why this
OL,13,FGovernment has been working closely
OL,14,Fwith forces to overcome these barriers
OL,15,Fto restore confidence in policing."
