OL,6,FNational Police Chiefs' Council lead
OL,7,Ffor vetting, Chief Constable Alex
OL,8,FFranklin-Smith, backed the changes,
OL,9,Fwhich "provide clear routes for action
OL,10,Fto remove individuals who fall below
OL,11,Fthe high standards the public and our
OL,12,Fworkforce rightly expect and deserve".
